s of the mug as well. If you are using a packet of hot chocolate mix instead, you can mix this with the hot milk. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNext, make your espresso. Pour the espresso shot into the prepared mug.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eNext, steam the milk. You want the milk hot and to create some foam on top. If your espresso machine has a frothing wand, you can do this all in one step. If not, you may need to heat the milk then froth by hand or use aÂ \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/47IdbwM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emilk frother\u003c/a\u003e. Add the hot chocolate mix during this step to incorporate well if using. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePour the hot milk into the espresso; the foam will naturally settle on top. Top with whipped cream, chocolate syrup and other garnishes. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/peppermint-mocha/?tp_image_id=119684\" data-pin-title=\"peppermint mocha\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-supplies-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/