content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/peppermint-mocha.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-120036\" data-recipe-id=\"120036\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"acf-helper-block_525c739eece95f043c1629c6851cd576\"\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGet our FREE recipe guide with our \u003cem\u003emost popular\u003c/em\u003e recipes of all time!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"#popup-1\" data-lity=\"\"\u003eGet the Guide\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIngredients\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"120036\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eshot\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eespresso\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 Â½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003emilk\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eÂ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epeppermint extract\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echocolate syrup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e(or a hot chocolate mix)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eÂ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ewhipped cream\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"120036\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eâ–¢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cp\u003eespresso maker\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eInstructions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"120036\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120036-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFirst, add the peppermint extract and chocolate syrup to your mug. I like to add most to the bottom, as it will mix with the hot espresso. But I will also drizzle some up the sides of the mug as well. If you are using a packet of hot chocolate mix instead, you can mix this with the hot milk.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120036-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, make your espresso. Pour the espresso shot into the prepared mug.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120036-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNext, steam the milk. You want the milk hot and to create some foam on top. If your espresso machine has a frothing wand, you can do this all in one step. If not, you may need to heat the milk then froth by hand or use aÂ \u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/47IdbwM\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emilk frother\u003c/a\u003e. Add the hot chocolate mix during this step to incorporate well if using.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120036-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePour the hot milk into the espresso; the foam will naturally settle on top.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120036-step-0-4\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTop with whipped cream, chocolate syrup and other garnishes.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eI also like to garnish this with a mini candy cane or crushed candy canes. Peppermint bark would be a nice addition too.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can use whole milk or any percentage; also, alternative milks will work well here too.Â \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdetails\u003e\n\n    \u003csummary\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cp\u003eNutrition Facts\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePeppermint Mocha\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAmount per Serving\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e% Daily Value*\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Percent Daily Values are based on a 2000 calorie diet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNotice: Nutrition is auto-calculated, using Spoonacular, for your convenience. Where relevant, we recommend using your own nutrition calculations.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/details\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
